description: '''Lisa Pin-Up''' (born '''Lisa Chilcott''') is a British [[electronic dance music]] producer and DJ, whose career started in the 1990s. She is a [[hard house]] producer and part of the [[Nukleuz]] [[record label|label]]. She is also a part-time model and ranked number 54 in ''[[Loaded (magazine)|Loaded]]''{{'s}} Hot 100 babes in 2002.
